''' Daybreak Game Company''' is a video game developer and based in San Diego. In [[2016]], it became the publisher of ''[[The Lord of the Rings Online]]'' with the transference from [[Warner Bros. Interactive Entertainment]].<ref>{{webcite|author=Bree Royce|articleurl=http://massivelyop.com/2016/12/19/turbine-spins-lotro-and-ddo-teams-out-to-new-studio-using-daybreak-as-publisher/|articlename= Turbine Spins ''Lord of the Rings Online'' and DDO Teams Out to New Studio, Using Daybreak As Publisher|dated=20 December 2016|website=[https://massivelyop.com/ Massivelyop]|accessed=25 January 2022}}</ref>
